Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief

Class Belief

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief.Belief
public class Belief extends Object
The Class Belief defines a data structure to store the agents information about the simulation.
Author:
Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution), Phil Heger (minor contribution)
